{"type": "article", "id": 28086, "title": "玻璃边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-13T07:00:03Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144920TpQ7AnGEWRdo2sCX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>现居意大利的产品设计师 <a href=\"http://www.saraferraridesign.com/\">Sara Ferrari </a>热衷于跨文化的研究，她最近为米兰公司 <a href=\"http://www.durame.it/\">Durame</a> 设计了这套 Tea 系列边桌，可以搭配出 48 种不同的风格。边桌由盖子和装饰瓶组成，这两部分均有不同的型号、颜色以及材质可选。作为底座的装饰瓶还可以当作容器用来收纳杂志之类的物件，不仅实用也非常美观，适用于各种室内环境。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021449183LDE0TsmOHGp42Pl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144919GuN29lAK3ItvgDyM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214491920NVWLMKnJFmcfvk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144919gD6fIso3kNRb8qXh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}